# Emergency Medical Services Unit Database (2026)

This project is a database system designed to manage Emergency Medical Services (EMS)
units, ambulances, staff, and emergency incidents efficiently.

## 📌 Project Overview
The Emergency Medical Services Unit Database aims to support EMS operations by organizing
data related to emergency calls, response times, ambulance deployment, and medical staff
assignments in a structured database.

## 🎯 Objectives
- Manage EMS units and ambulances
- Track emergency calls and incidents
- Record response times
- Organize EMS staff assignments
- Support data analysis and reporting

